<div class="tldr"><div class="tldr-label">TL;DR</div><p>This calculator estimates the end-to-end Year 1 cash cost of setting up an Insurance Marketing Firm registered with <a href="https://irdai.gov.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline">IRDAI</a> under the <em>IRDAI (Registration of Insurance Marketing Firm) Regulations, 2015</em>. Typical Year 1 cash cost: <strong>₹1.5 lakh to ₹3.5 lakh</strong> covering MCA registration, IRDAI ₹5,000 application fee, professional services, Principal Officer + ISP training, office infrastructure, Professional Indemnity Insurance, and first-year statutory compliance. <strong>Net worth</strong> (₹10 lakh for smaller cities, ₹50 lakh for larger urban) is a separate capital requirement, not an expense — it remains parked in the IMF as paid-up capital plus reserves.</p></div>

